text: Arthur Blickenstorfer (20 April 1935 - 27 October 2001) was a Swiss equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1935 births Category:2001 deaths Category:Swiss male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Switzerland Category:Equestrians at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:People from the canton of Zürich
